Yemen Poised to Pick Leader, From Slate of One
ADEN, Yemenâ€”Yemenis go to the polls Tuesday to fill out presidential ballots that will bear just one name, in what will be the first significant test of the internationally sponsored transfer of power deal hashed out by the country's political elite.
